he's on top of it's hate lists.  And the chase is on again.  And it so happens while chasing it, you will agro other mobs just like him now you have 2 or more of these kiting mobs to worry about... <br><br>I think this would be a very interesting mob to think about for Luclin. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyofallien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yofallien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/2/01 4:04:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=128.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Mob Idea:Kiting Mob</span><hr size=1> Only hole...would be root or snare.  Nothing breaks a kite attempt like catching yourself with BoF.  (Naw I don't use AtoL's fizzles too much) To keep the principle working the Mob would have to have high MR.  I'm not sure I would welcome the change on a large scale.  But might be fun to poke around with.  Great Idea!! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaniar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aniar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/6/01 12:09:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=128.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Mob Idea:Kiting Mob</span><hr size=1> It'd make us a little more liked in groups I think - when he stops to nuke, so does the wizard who he's trying to kite.  Cleric follows the wizard to keep him from being stomped...  that'd be kinda like fear kiting...? <p><br>Aniar Orrenson<br>Wizard of the 29th Season<br>High Councilman of the Nightwatch of Norrath<br>"You look up overkill in the dictionary and there's a picture of Aniar lol" Lotta on Saryrn</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showPrevMessage?topicID=128.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showNextMessage?topicID=128.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=128.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.emailToFriend?topicID=128.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.threadControl?topicID=128.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=128.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=128.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table bor